window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Thomas Pynchon has a reputation as a \"difficult\" author - but he doesn't have to be! With this new guide, <i>Gravity's Rainbow</i> can be understood by the average listener. Included are: a chapter-by-chapter summary and commentary on the story, a thorough description of all major characters, a biography of Pynchon, suggestions for essay topics, and much more. This guide is guaranteed to help you finish and make sense of Gravity's Rainbow - all in a concise and easy format. Whether you are totally new to the book or just want to deepen your understanding, this guide will save you hours of struggle and frustration. </p>"; 
